{"id": 1106, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于女生化妆，你有什么困惑？", "description": "女生的困惑：我怎么画这么丑；男生的困惑：她怎么画这么久？（题图来自：Milo Lockett）", "record_count": 2480, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160710221434Ccxt6GpmoSBTriZL.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-14T03:00:25Z", "options": [{"id": 97792, "content": "真的很“一”的一字眉", "image": null, "praise_count": 158, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651447}, {"id": 97798, "content": "画了妆的叫妖，素颜的叫素颜婊。让不让人活", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 629807}, {"id": 97799, "content": "哇擦，脖子也要涂白一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678602}, {"id": 97801, "content": "夏天到底怎么化才不会糊一脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 264156}, {"id": 97802, "content": "讨厌大眼影，跟鬼一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675797}, {"id": 97805, "content": "把这个妆洗下去，会是另外一个人吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 97806, "content": "我妹向我推荐妆前乳，妆前乳是嘛？就是用妆前乳可以不用隔离..?有区别么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615403}, {"id": 97807, "content": "化了妆也没人家素颜漂亮。怪我手残还是怪我丑？", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238743}, {"id": 97808, "content": "女人就该注重脸蛋，之前脸上各种问题，斑点，痘痘，邹纹，皮肤暗黄，现在皮夫滑滑的水嫩嫩的，自信心也回来了，再也不怕出门需要低头走路了，感激我的好闺蜜，她给我介绍了一个导师的空间?里面挺多东西学习的，也有护理导师的指导Q号 861301814\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678608}, {"id": 97809, "content": "化妆化的太美、男生会不会很反感", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678615}, {"id": 97810, "content": "女友对我说说这个口红真好，涂了像没有涂一样，我问她为什么要买这个 ，然后没然后了", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649108}, {"id": 99602, "content": "我只想问，那是你吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683498}, {"id": 97811, "content": "每次出门都要等个一两小时?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127093}, {"id": 97813, "content": "怎么也不敢画内眼线，分分钟怕戳瞎自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678636}, {"id": 97815, "content": "丑人多作怪", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663476}, {"id": 107544, "content": "为什么一定要化妆？真天然不好吗？好吧我以后可能也会化的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711274}, {"id": 97817, "content": "今天换了支口红色，你觉得怎样？“好看好看”？？？？（os:看不出来差别）\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611598}, {"id": 97818, "content": "为什么很多妹子可以在摇摇晃晃的公共交通上画眼线和睫毛膏，一个急刹车不会戳到眼睛吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454428}, {"id": 100379, "content": "为什么腮红永远画的像高原红", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687115}, {"id": 97820, "content": "会化妆的都很厉害", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678651}, {"id": 97822, "content": "坏化完妆以后就想减肥了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 521512}, {"id": 97823, "content": "为什么要那么多口红。我感觉颜色都一样呀！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677418}, {"id": 97826, "content": "画得好是天仙，画得差是女鬼", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 570505}, {"id": 97828, "content": "化妆品为什么能细分这么多种", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536471}, {"id": 97829, "content": "这一堆瓶瓶罐罐都什么鬼！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 97830, "content": "化不化的，关键还是看胚子，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 97831, "content": "人丑不要紧，还化成鬼出来吓人，就是你不对了，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 100647, "content": "脸怎么抹才不会太白。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688336}, {"id": 97832, "content": "为什么要化妆？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669795}, {"id": 97833, "content": "口红这么多颜色，都是号数命名，怎么记得住色？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 441930}, {"id": 99369, "content": "为什么差距会这么大？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296381}, {"id": 97835, "content": "画了妆就是出去浪～～谁说的！！我们只是心情好", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674451}, {"id": 97836, "content": "没有困惑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365693}, {"id": 99628, "content": "我只想说，这是你吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683498}, {"id": 97837, "content": "黄子华：你卸了妆我认得你叫化妆，你卸了妆我不认得你，那叫乔装。", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251803}, {"id": 106797, "content": "就算不打粉底，不涂口红，不画眼线，也要摸个防晒霜或BB霜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711860}, {"id": 97838, "content": "媳妇，帮我也化化？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511481}, {"id": 97839, "content": "到底打底是神马？定妆又是神马??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678691}, {"id": 97840, "content": "化了之后别人竟然看不出来?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673356}, {"id": 97841, "content": "为什么我画了阴影，脸还是那么大？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669957}, {"id": 99889, "content": "我说的可能和很多人不一样吧，本来化妆就感觉很装", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 505318}, {"id": 97842, "content": "一张脸要涂十几层 好可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532476}, {"id": 97843, "content": "手残是重点，一样的护肤品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656148}, {"id": 97844, "content": "手残是重点，一样的化妆品", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656148}, {"id": 97845, "content": "眼影画出来都一个样，买那么多干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229855}, {"id": 97846, "content": "为什么总是缺一样化妆品", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650227}, {"id": 97847, "content": "为什么戴假睫毛", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678724}, {"id": 97848, "content": "画浓眉代表了什么审美？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224481}, {"id": 97850, "content": "浪费时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416095}, {"id": 103738, "content": "咋化妆，这些个真的是笔吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699578}]}